cat
(defsource x [int32 int64])
----
ok

# both have limit and offset

build apply=Fusion
(top_k (top_k (get x) [] [] 3 2) [] [] 1 1)
----
%0 =
| Get x (u0)
| TopK group=() order=() limit=1 offset=3

